ind%20that%20can%20mean%20the%20difference%20between%20early%20intervention%20and%20irreversible%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20conditions%2C%20%26quot%3Bspeed%20is%20the%20most%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Choi%20said.%20That's%20true%20for%20%26quot%3Bsilent%20killers%26quot%3B%20like%20heart%20and%20kidney%20disease%2C%20and%20progressive%20conditions%20like%20glaucoma%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20often%20show%20no%20early%20symptoms%20but%2C%20unchecked%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20permanent%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20patients%20with%20chronic%20conditions%20like%20diabetes%20or%20obesity%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20even%20higher.%20Early%20complications%20can%20lead%20to%20dementia%2C%20liver%20disease%2C%20heart%20problems%2C%20or%20kidney%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20these%20risks%20are%20spotted%2C%20the%20more%20options%20doctors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20patients%20%E2%80%94%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20said%20Mediwhale's%20AI%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20triage%20by%20flagging%20who's%20low-risk%2C%20who%20needs%20monitoring%2C%20and%20who%20should%20see%20a%20doctor%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScreening%20patients%20at%20the%20first%20point%20of%20contact%20doesn't%20require%20%26quot%3Bvery%20deep%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20Choi%20said.%20That%20kind%20of%20quick%2C%20low-friction%20risk%20assessment%20is%20where%20AI%20shines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMediwhale's%20tool%20lets%20patients%20bypass%20traditional%20procedures%20%E2%80%94%20including%20blood%20tests%2C%20CT%20scans%2C%20and%20ultrasounds%20%E2%80%94%20when%20screening%20for%20cardiovascular%20and%20kidney%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20also%20said%20that%20when%20patients%20see%20their%20risks%20visualized%20through%20retinal%20scans%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20take%20it%20more%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a6e82c9-5653-43cb-9854-889678e78257%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226014%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Choi%20on%20the%20street%20in%20Seou