0and%20the%20sea%20breeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20landed%20on%20Sicily%20and%20chose%20a%20quaint%20seafront%20hotel%20in%20Giardini%20Naxos%2C%20located%20just%20north%20of%20Catania.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20perfect%20location%20and%20time%20of%20year%20to%20visit%2C%20especially%20with%20my%20grandmother's%20age%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20needs%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20two%20international%20airports%20located%20in%20Catania%20and%20Palermo%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20convenient%20railway%20system%20and%20a%20comprehensive%20bus%20network%20running%20across%20the%20island%2C%20Sicily%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20get%20to%20%E2%80%94%20and%20just%20as%20easy%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20direct%20bus%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20town%2C%20giving%20my%20grandmother%20a%20chance%20to%20soak%20in%20the%20views%20and%20snap%20photos%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1cdf07c-02ef-41e7-9c41-f9b5d41923ab%5C%22%3EMay%20was%20the%20perfect%20time%20to%20enjoy%20warm%20weather%20with%20fewer%20crowds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221854%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20from%20Villa%20Communale%2C%20the%20park%20in%20Taormina%2C%20Sicily.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862a8e0f748d8c055f4a2f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221232%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20Taormina's%20public%20garden%20was%20unforgettable.%3Cp%3EGloria%20Kostadinova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20was%20warm%20enough%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20pool%20at%20our%20hotel%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20sweltering%20Sicilian%20sun%20of%20the%20mid-summer%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20wasn't%20peak%20season%2C%20the%20town%20had%20a%20relaxing%20feel%20with%20fewer%20tourists%20and%20crowds%20than%20we%20might've%20seen%20at%20a%20different%20time.%20We%20never%20had%20to%20wait%20in%20long%20l