nessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-things-to-get-at-seafood-restaurant-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efresh%20seafood%20dishes%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20pasta%20alle%20vongole%20(pasta%20with%20clams).%20Although%20she%20didn't%20partake%2C%20my%20grandmother%20admired%20my%20husband's%20adventurous%20appetite%20when%20he%20tried%20ricci%20di%20mare%20(sea%20urchins)%2C%20a%20Sicilian%20delicacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20over%20the%20island%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20striking%20ceramic%20heads%20of%20a%20man%20and%20woman%20(teste%20di%20moro)%2C%20often%20in%20the%20form%20of%20vases.%20Deeply%20rooted%20in%20Sicilian%20folklore%2C%20the%20heads%20have%20various%20stories%20explaining%20their%20origins%2C%20mostly%20involving%20themes%20of%20love%20and%20betrayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20remember%20our%20trip%2C%20my%20grandmother%20and%20I%20bought%20small%20ceramic%20pine%20cones%2C%20another%20powerful%20symbol%20in%20Sicilian%20culture%2C%20representing%20prosperity%20and%20good%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f8895f7-b345-41b8-a04b-8afd9deadd3f%5C%22%3EMaking%20my%20grandmother%20smile%20on%20her%20birthday%20was%20the%20greatest%20gift%20of%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22914%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20and%20her%20grandmother%20in%20Sicily.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862ab8b85e81483682d0a32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20best%20part%20of%20my%20trip%20to%20Sicily%20was%20spending%20time%20with%20my%20grandmother.%3Cp%3EGloria%20Kostadinova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20her%20first%20birthday%20without%20my%20grandfather%2C%20it%20was%20a%20beautiful%20experience%20for%20all%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20grandmother%2C%20it%20meant%20not%20feeling%20alone%20in%20her%20grief%20and%20fulfilling%20a%20lifelong%20dream%20to%20visit%20Italy.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20meant%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2