at%20stayed%20with%20me%20long%20after%20I%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMore%20restaurants%20had%20vegetarian%20options%20than%20I%20expected.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interior%20of%20a%20pub%20with%20flags%20hung%20from%20ceiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed1b5f748d8c055f489a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20online%20menus%20didn't%20seem%20vegetarian-friendly%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20options%20once%20I%20asked%20in%20real%20life.%3Cp%3EAlesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20vegetarian%2C%20I%20came%20in%20with%20pretty%20low%20expectations%20for%20the%20variety%20of%20foods%20I'd%20get%20to%20eat%20when%20it%20came%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-go-in-ireland-not-dublin-tips-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edining%20out%20in%20Dublin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Local%20cuisine%20tends%20to%20rely%20heavily%20on%20meat%2C%20from%20Irish%20breakfasts%20to%20pies%20and%20stews.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20menus%20I%20browsed%20had%20lots%20of%20meat%20dishes%20and%20it%20initially%20looked%20like%20plant-based%20options%20would%20be%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20However%2C%20once%20I%20asked%20restaurant%20staff%20in%20person%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20accommodating%20most%20places%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20servers%20brought%20out%20full%20vegetarian%20menus%20that%20weren't%20printed%20and%20only%20available%20to%20customers%20who%20requested%20them.%20Others%20happily%20offered%20to%20have%20something%20special%20prepared%20from%20the%20kitchen%20or%20make%20vegetarian-friendly%20menu%20swaps.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELocal%20tipping%20culture%20felt%20more%20low-key%20than%20what%20I%20was%20used%20to%20back%20home.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Alesandra%20D