0the%20cleanest%20I've%20seen%20in%20a%20major%20European%20city.%20This%20was%20an%20especially%20impressive%20feat%2C%20given%20that%20I%20visited%20the%20city%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-patricks-day-celebrated-differences-ireland-us-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESt.%20Patrick's%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20had%20hosted%20a%20massive%20parade%20and%20beers%20and%20crowds%20spilled%20out%20of%20every%20pub%20the%20cleanup%20was%20surprisingly%20swift%20and%20civilized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20expecting%20a%20bit%20more%20grit%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20high-traffic%20areas%20around%20the%20city%20center%20or%20Temple%20Bar%20%E2%80%94%20but%20even%20those%20looked%20remarkably%20tidy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESidewalks%20were%20free%20of%20litter%2C%20public%20trash%20bins%20weren't%20overflowing%2C%20and%20I%20never%20once%20encountered%20the%20kind%20of%20mess%20that%20can%20be%20common%20outside%20of%20crowded%2C%20late-night%20spots.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20city%20with%20so%20much%20foot%20traffic%20(and%20so%20many%20pubs)%2C%20it%20was%20honestly%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20city%20feels%20cozy%20and%20cosmopolitan%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Alesandra%20Dubin%20sitting%20at%20a%20picnic%20table%20outside%20of%20a%20building%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed24c85e81483682cf0b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20fun%20to%20step%20away%20to%20spots%20like%20Avoca%20Mill.%20%3Cp%3EAlesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDublin%20hits%20that%20rare%20sweet%20spot%3A%20it's%20a%20capital%20city%20with%20real%20cultural%20and%20historical%20heft%2C%20but%20it%20still%20feels%20approachable%20and%20easy%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20greater%20area%20population%20around%20a%20million%20(and%20a%20Dublin%20city%20population%20substantially%20smaller)%2C%20I%20never%20felt%20overwhelmed%20by%20crowds%20or%20traffic.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20many%20major%20sights%20were%20walkable.%20Even%20when%20the%20city%20center%20was%20packed%20for%20the%20holiday%20events%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20navigate%20in%20and%20around%20the%20area.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20trouble%20making%20my%20way%20to%20several%20sights%20outside%20the%20urban%20area%2C%20from%20Avoca%20Mill%20(the%20country's%20oldest%20working%20hand-weaving%20mill)%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-colors-analyzed-by-pro-told-me-what-to-wear-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKildare%20Village%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20luxury%20shopping%20outpost).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20strong%20creative%20energy%20in%20the%20air%20%E2%80%94%20from%20bookstores%20and%20galleries%20to%20street%20musicians%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20overall%20pace%20is%20slower%20and%20more%20relaxed%20than%20what%20I've%20experienced%20in%20bigger%20European%20capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-going-to-dublin-first-time-from-american-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751805841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ed3b085e81483682cf100%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-going-to-dublin-first-time-from-american-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20an%20American%2C%20my%20first%20trip%20to%20Dublin%20was%20filled%20with%20surprises%20about%20locals%2C%20tipping%20culture%2C%20vegetarian%20options%2C%20and%20more%20parts%20of%20the%20Irish%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehochberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Alesandra%20Dubin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business